Installation of Z3
==================

Documentation as of 20 Nov, 2012.

1. `git clone https://git01.codeplex.com/z3`
   You will need Git 1.7.10 or later.

2. Move to Z3 directory (assume $Z3DIR), patch the difference against 'master'
   branch by `patch -p1 < $(Yhorn)/z3_patch.diff`

3. Follow README 2) for building Z3.

4. `cd $Z3DIR/src/api/ml`

5. `chmod 755 *.sh`

6. `./build-lib.sh`

7. `./install-lib.sh`
